      "content": "Hey, I'm working with some execs who are prepping for some really high-stakes boardroom meetings and investor pitches. Can you give me some general advice on grooming and appearance for them? I want to make sure they're projecting as much authority and professionalism as possible. Like, what should they be focusing on regarding hair, makeup, and overall look to hit that \"leader\" vibe?",
