      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That \"polished\" and \"controlled\" look makes sense. Can you get a bit more specific with the grooming side of things? For instance, when it comes to hair, what kind of styles or textures are generally considered the most \"authoritative\" or \"standard\" for a professional setting? I want to make sure everyone's hair looks aligned with that high-level image.",
